  <prompt>
Validate the prototype UAT harness framework by standing up `smart-todo-r4-uat/` as its first consumer. Mount the production SmartTodoWidget against mocked Xrm + seeded sprk_todo data. Sub-second visual iteration on widget changes without the master-deploy cycle.
  </prompt>

  <role>
Cross-repo dev. Comfortable editing in BOTH `spaarke-wt-smart-todo-r4` (production source) and `spaarke-prototype` (sandbox harness).
  </role>

  <goal>
A working `npm run dev` at `c:/code_files/spaarke-prototype/projects/smart-todo-r4-uat/` that renders the SmartTodoWidget with realistic mock data, and HMR-reloads when the widget source files in `spaarke-wt-smart-todo-r4` are edited. Closes the iteration-time gap that drove Wave D + Wave E rework loops.
  </goal>

